column2: SELECT s.specObjID, g.class, g.subClass, g.z, g.ra, g.dec, g.plate, g.fiberID, g.MJD, s.oii_#_flux as OII3#, s.oiii_#_flux as OIII4#, s.oiii_#_flux as OIII5#, s.h_beta_flux as HBeta, s.h_alpha_flux as HAlpha, s.nii_#_flux as NII6#, FROM galSpecLine s JOIN specObj g ON g.specObjID = s.specObjID WHERE g.plate = # AND g.fiberID = #
